s%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsouth-africa-vs-australia-semi-final-live-updates-world-cup-2023-4578252%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsouth-africa-vs-australia-semi-final-live-updates-world-cup-2023-4578252%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsouth-africa-vs-australia-semi-final-live-updates-world-cup-2023-4578252%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Biden-Xi%20Deal%20On%20Fentanyl%2C%20Cause%20Of%2070%2C000%20Deaths%20In%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnited%20States%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20said%20Wednesday%20China%20had%20re-committed%20itself%20to%20tackling%20the%20flow%20of%20fentanyl%20-%20a%20synthetic%20opioid%20responsible%20for%20over%2070%2C000%20drug%20overdose%20deaths%20in%20the%20US%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20-%20arrived%20at%20as%20Mr%20Biden%20and%20China's%20Xi%20Jinping%20met%20in%20San%20Francisco%20on%20the%20side-lines%20of%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation%20Summit%20-%20is%20key%20because%20Beijing%20had%20earlier%20refused%20to%20hold%20talks%20on%20the%20supply%20of%20fentanyl%20unless%20the%20US%20lifts%20restrictions%20on%20its%20Institute%20of%20Forensic%20Science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20providing%20anti-drug%20agencies%20a%20boost%2C%20the%20agreement%20will%20also%20help%20Biden%20ward%20off%20attacks%20from%20the%20Republicans%2C%20who%20have%20complained%20the%20US%20isn't%20doing%20enough%20to%20stop%20the%20fentanyl%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFentanyl%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20major%20issue%20in%20next%20year's%20presidential%20election%20either%20way.%20If%20it%20is%20stopped%20Biden%20will%20claim%20a%20win%20in%20the%20war%20on%20drugs.%20If%20it%20is%20not%20then%20the%20Republicans%20will%20have%20more%20ammo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EUS-China%20Fentanyl%20Agreement%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBasically%2C%20after%20initiating%20crackdowns%20five-six%20years%20ago%20on%20companies%20exporting%20finished%20versions%20of%20the%20drug%2C%20China%20is%20now%20expected%20to%20also%20target%20those%20making%20precursor%20chemicals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20said%20the%20renewed%20agreement%20will%20also%20focus%20on%20evolving%20strategies%20to%20not%20only%20counter%20the%20creation%20and%20distribution%20of%20newer%20illicit%20synthetic%20drugs%20but%2C%20critically%2C%20also%20to%20reduce%20the%20diversion%20of%20precursor%20chemicals%20and%20pill%20presses%20to%20drug%20cartels%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20going%20to%20save%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Biden%20said%2C%20hours%20before%20Mr%20Jinping%20said%20China%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20sympathises%26quot%3B%20with%20American%20people%20for%20%26quot%3Bthe%20suffering%20fentanyl%20has%20inflicted%20upon%20them%26quot%3B.%20However%2C%20in%20a%20caveat%20underlining%20the%20mutual%20distrust%2C%20the%20US%20is%20expected%20to%20%26quot%3Btrust%20but%20verify%26quot%3B%20China's%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20backwards%20from%20Wednesday's%20deal%2C%20last%20month%20six%20American%20senators%20-%20three%20Republicans%20and%20three%20Democrats%2C%20including%20Senate%20Majority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%20-%20visited%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20Mr%20Jinping%20did%20not%20outright%20refuse%20talks%20on%20fentanyl%20gave%20the%20American%20side%20hope%2C%20but%20the%20forensics%20institute%20issue%20remained%20a%20stumbling%20block%2C%20global%20media%20reports%20indicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20murmurs%20of%20disagreement%2C%20including%20when%20Chinese%20government%20spokespersons%20said%20the%20Americans%20ought%20not%20to%20blame%20others%20for%20their%20own%20policy%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senators'%20visit%20was%20shortly%20after%20the%20US%20government%20indicted%20and%20charged%20eight%20Chinese%20companies%20and%20numerous%20executives%20for%20importing%20the%20precursor%20chemicals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EUS-China%20Fentanyl%20Story%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMexico%20and%20China%20are%20the%20primary%20sources%20for%20fentanyl%20and%20fentanyl-related%20substances%20trafficked%20directly%20into%20the%20U.S.%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Drug%20Enforcement%20Administration.%20However%2C%20nearly%20all%20the%20precursor%20chemicals%20come%20from%20China%20and%20are%20often%20falsely%20packaged%20to%20avoid%20detection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%20the%20Chinese%20government%20announced%20a%20series%20of%20steps%20to%20combat%20the%20export%20of%20fentanyl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20after%20a%20meeting%20between%20Mr%20Jinping%20and%20then%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump.%20Crucially%2C%20China%20said%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Bagreed%20to%20designate%20fentanyl%20as%20a%20controlled%20substance%26quot%3B%20and%2C%20over%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20crackdowns%20across%20China%20became%20evident%2C%20and%20supply%20to%20the%20US%20fell%20drastically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing's%20crackdown%20widened%20to%20include%20variants%2C%20like%20carfentanil%2C%20after%20it%20was%20found%20manufacturers%20were%20exploiting%20loopholes%20by%20marginally%20altering%20the%20chemical%20structure%20of%20the%20opioid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%2C%20after%20urging%20from%20Mr%20Trump%2C%20moved%20to%20block%20these%20loopholes.%20Since%20then%2C%20though%2C%20the%20shipments%20are%20being%20increasingly%20routed%20via%20the%20Mexico%20border.%20The%20US%20is%20already%20in%20talks%20with%20Mexican%20officials%20to%20shut%20down%20this%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20Is%20Fentanyl%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPharmaceutical%20fentanyl%20is%20100%20times%20more%20potent%20than%20morphine%20and%2050%20times%20more%20so%20than%20heroin%2C%20and%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20US'%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20as%20an%20analgesic%20(pain%20relief)%20in%201998.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20street%20it%20is%20also%20called%20China%20Girl%20and%20China%20Town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFentanyl%2C%20like%20other%20opioid%20analgesics%2C%20leads%20to%20euphoria%2C%20pain%20relief%2C%20sedation%2C%20confusion%2C%20drowsiness%2C%20nausea%2C%20and%20vomiting%2C%20as%20well%20as%20urinary%20retention%2C%20pupillary%20constriction%2C%20and%20respiratory%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20has%20labelled%20fentanyl%20and%20fentanyl-laced%20drugs%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20dangerous%26quot%3B%2C%20warning%20many%20may%20even%20be%20unaware%20their%20drugs%20are%20laced%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20CDC%2C%20some%20of%20the%20signs%20of%20a%20fentanyl%20overdose%20are%20constricted%20pupils%2C%20weak%20or%20slow%20breathing%2C%20choking%20or%20gurgling%20sounds%2C%20a%20limp%20body%20and%20discoloured%20or%20cold%2C%20or%20clammy%2C%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700125440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fb0o84s4_fentanyl-pill_625x300_16_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffentanyl-us-china-talks-biden-xi-jinping-ndtv-explains-what-is-fentanyl-synthetic-opioid-discussed-by-biden-xi-4578606%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22United%20States%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20said%20Wednesday%20China%20will%20take%20steps%20to%20tackle%20the%20flow%20of%20fentanyl%20-%20a%20synthetic%20opioid%20responsible%20for%20the%20death%20of%20over%2070%2C000%20people%20last%20year%20-%20into%20the%2