rd%20of%20mouth.%20No%20amount%20of%20ad%20spends%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F81VRpdYsoz%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F81VRpdYsoz%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Ritesh%20Agarwal%20(%40riteshagar)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Friteshagar%2Fstatus%2F1724727250505937338%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWord-of-mouth%20marketing%2C%20considered%20a%20powerful%20tool%20in%20business%2C%20relies%20on%20audiences%20that%20organically%20share%20the%20word%20about%20brands.%20The%20tactic%20is%20used%20to%20generate%20natural%20discussions%20about%20and%20recommendations%20for%20a%20product%20or%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20users%20agreed%20with%20Mr%C2%A0Agarwal%20and%20posted%20a%20variety%20of%20comments%20in%20response.%C2%A0One%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Word%20of%20mouth%20remains%20unparalleled%20in%20its%20influence%20and%20impact!''%20Another%20said%2C%20''Yadav%20ji%20was%20so%20bang-on-target!''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entrepreneur%2C%20now%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20youngest%20billionaires%2C%20founded%20OYO%20when%20he%20was%20just%2019%20years%20old.%20Oyo%20Rooms%2C%20which%20specialises%20in%20no-frills%20accommodation%2C%20was%20formed%20in%202013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Oyo%20teams%20up%20with%20owners%20of%20budget%20hotels%20to%20help%20connect%20them%20with%20tourists%20looking%20for%20cheap%20but%20clean%20accommodation%20that%20meets%20certain%20hygiene%20standards.%20OYO%20now%20operates%20in%20over%20800%20cities%20in%2080%20countries%20and%20is%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20fastest-growing%20hotel%20chains%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Travelling%20across%20India%20at%20the%20age%20of%2017%2C%20Ritesh%20stayed%20in%20more%20than%20100%20bed%20and%20breakfasts%2C%20guest%20houses%2C%20and%20hotels%20to%20realize%20there%20was%20a%20massive%20dearth%20of%20affordable%20and%20