nconscious%20and%20unresponsive%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20alley%2C%20and%20an%20individual%20transported%20him%20to%20Rancho%20High%20School%2C%20as%20explained%20by%20Lieutenant%20Johansson.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20he%20was%20admitted%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20where%20it%20was%20swiftly%20determined%20that%20he%20had%20sustained%20%26quot%3Bnonsurvivable%20head%20trauma%26quot%3B%20shortly%20after%20his%20arrival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20days%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20his%20family%20said%20that%20he%20was%20declared%20mentally%20brain-dead.%20His%20family%20decided%20to%20donate%20his%20organs.%20The%20cause%20of%20death%20was%20blunt%20force%20trauma%2C%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700118660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fi4t9v2sg_jonathan-lewis-jr_625x300_16_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Feight-teens-accused-of-murder-in-fatal-beating-of-17-year-old-schoolmate-in-us-4578603%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lt.%20Jason%20Johansson%20stated%20that%20the%20altercation%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20originated%20from%20a%20dispute%20over%20a%20pair%20of%20stolen%20headphones.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Feight-teens-accused-of-murder-in-fatal-beating-of-17-year-old-schoolmate-in-us-4578603%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Feight-teens-accused-of-murder-in-fatal-beating-of-17-year-old-schoolmate-in-us-4578603%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Feight-teens-accused-of-murder-in-fatal-beating-of-17-year-old-schoolmate-in-us-4578603%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SRK%20cheers%20for%20Team%20India%20for%20World%20Cup%20Finals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700118447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F