wo%20sides%20also%20reached%20an%20agreement%20to%20curb%20to%20cooperate%20on%20tackling%20the%20supply%20of%20fentanyl%2C%20a%20leading%20cause%20of%20drug%20overdoses%20in%20the%20US.%20Under%20the%20pact%2C%20China%20will%20go%20directly%20after%20chemical%20companies%20that%20make%20fentanyl%20precursors.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EArtificial%20Intelligence%20also%20figured%20in%20the%20talks.%20A%20White%20House%20readout%20of%20the%20meeting%20said%20%26quot%3Bthe%20leaders%20affirmed%20the%20need%20to%20address%20the%20risks%20of%20advanced%20AI%20systems%20and%20improve%20AI%20safety%20through%20US-China%20government%20talks%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20months%20ahead%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20preserve%20and%20pursue%20high-level%20diplomacy%20with%20the%20PRC%20in%20both%20directions%2C%20to%20keep%20the%20lines%20of%20communication%20open%2C%20including%20between%20President%20Xi%20and%20me.%20He%20and%20I%20agreed%20that%20each%20one%20of%20us%20could%20pick%20up%20the%20phone%2C%20call%20directly%20and%20we'd%20be%20heard%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20there%20was%20a%20long%20list%20of%20memorable%20quotes.%20Xi%20said%20%26quot%3Bplanet%20earth%20is%20big%20enough%20for%20the%20two%20countries%20to%20succeed%26quot%3B.%20Biden%20said%20the%20world%20expects%20the%20US%20and%20China%20to%20manage%20%26quot%3Bcompetition%20responsibly%26quot%3B%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20veering%20into%20%26quot%3Bconflict%2C%20confrontation%2C%20or%20a%20new%20Cold%20War%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20were%20light%20moments%20too.%20Biden%20reminded%20Xi%20of%20his%20wife%20Peng%20Liyuan's%20birthday%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20his%20birthday%20too.%20The%20embarrassed%20Chinese%20president%20said%20he%20had%20been%20neck-deep%20in%20work%20and%20the%20date%20had%20slipped%20his%20mind.%20He%20thanked%20Biden%20for%20the%20timely%20reminder.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20was%20not%20all%20smiles%20and%20handshakes%20though.%20Biden%20raised%20concerns%20about%20alleged%20human%20rights%20abuses%20by%20China%20in%20Xinjiang%2C%20Tibet%20and%20Hong%20Kong.%20%26quot%3BI%20gave%20them%20names%20of%20individuals%20that%20we%20think%20are%20being%20held%2C%20and%20hopefully%2C%20we%20can%20get%20them%20released%20as%20well.%20No%20agreement%20on%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said%20later.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Taiwan%20issue%20came%20up%20too.%20When%20Biden%20raised%20the%20subject%2C%20Xi%20firmly%20said%20the%20US%20must%20stop%20arming%20the%20island%20and%20stressed%20that%20reunification%20was%20%26quot%3Bunstoppable%26quot%3B.%20Beijing%20claims%20sovereignty%20over%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESoon%20after%20the%20meeting%2C%20Biden%20went%20off%20the%20script%20with%20a%20remark%20that%20will%20not%20amuse%20China.%20Referring%20to%20Xi%2C%20he%20told%20the%20media%2C%20%26quot%3BHe's%20a%20dictator%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20he's%20a%20guy%20who%20runs%20a%20country%20that%20is%20a%20communist%20country%20that's%20based%20on%20a%20form%20of%20government%20totally%20different%20than%20ours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700117100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fjkb9b4q_xi-biden-reuters_625x300_16_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fxi-jinping-joe-biden-handshakes-smiles-and-pacts-at-biden-xi-meet-and-new-cold-war-warning-4578502%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20significant%20meeting%20between%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20his%20Chinese%20counterpart%20Xi%20Jinping%20in%20San%20Francisco%20saw%20several%20milestones%20and%20a%20few%20roadblocks%20as%20the%20superpowers%20agreed%20that%20turning%20their%20backs%20on%20each%20other%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20an%20option%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld