the%20two%20years%20preceding%20her%20demise%2C%20as%20outlined%20in%20the%20criminal%20complaint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20charges%2C%20Kurczewski%20entered%20a%20plea%20of%20not%20guilty%20to%20first-degree%20intentional%20homicide%20and%20two%20counts%20of%20felony%20theft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%203%2C%202018%2C%20Hernan%20was%20discovered%20unconscious%20in%20her%20living%20room%20recliner%20beside%20a%20table%20strewn%20with%20prescription%20pills%2C%20some%20of%20which%20seemed%20to%20be%20crushed%20on%20her%20chest%2C%20as%20detailed%20in%20a%20police%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%20classified%20as%20a%20drug%20overdose%2C%20Kurczewski%2C%20identified%20as%20Hernan's%20friend%20and%20caregiver%2C%20contacted%20the%20police%20to%20report%20finding%20her%20unresponsive%20and%20without%20signs%20of%20breathing%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%20Allegedly%2C%20Kurczewski%20informed%20the%20police%20that%20she%20suspected%20Hernan's%20health%20conditions%20had%20led%20to%20suicidal%20thoughts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApproximately%20three%20months%20following%20Hernan's%20death%2C%20the%20Waukesha%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office%20resumed%20the%20investigation%20upon%20the%20revelation%20of%20a%20toxicological%20report%20indicating%20a%20lethal%20quantity%20of%20tetrahydrozoline%2C%20the%20primary%20component%20in%20over-the-counter%20eye%20drops%2C%20in%20Hernan's%20system%2C%20as%20outlined%20in%20the%20criminal%20complaint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKurczewski%20was%20arrested%20and%20formally%20charged%20in%20June%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FUS%2Fwisconsin-woman-found-guilty-killing-friend-eye-drops%2Fstory%3Fid%3D104887158%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EABC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20throughout%20the%20extensive%20trial%20spanning%20several%20weeks%2C%20the%20prosecution%20contended%20that%20Kurczewski%20stood%20as%20one%20of%20the%20recipients%20outlined%20in%20Hernan's%20will%2C%20asserting%20that%2C%20in%20the%20defendant's%20perspective%2C%20%26quot%3BLynn%20Hernan%20became%20worth%20more%20dead%20than%20alive.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20defence%20argued%20against%20the%20notion%20that%20Kurczewski%20poisoned%20Hernan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20just%20liked%20vodka.%20She%20also%20liked%20Visine.%20I%20have%20no%20idea%20why%2C%26quot%3B%20defence%20attorney%20Pablo%20Galaviz%20said%20of%20Hernan%20during%20opening%20statements%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecutors%20expressed%20they%20were%20satisfied%20with%20the%20guilty%20verdict%2C%20and%20said%20the%20medical%20examiner's%20work%20provided%20%26quot%3Bvital%20evidence%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20defendant%20betrayed%20Lynn%20out%20of%20greed%2C%26quot%3B%20Waukesha%20County%20Deputy%20District%20Attorney%20Abbey%20Nickolie%20told%20reporters%20following%20the%20verdict.%20%26quot%3BThis%20case%20highlighted%20the%20financial%20vulnerability%20of%20the%20victim%20and%20what%20a%20person%20would%20do%20to%20get%20what%20they%20want.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700114160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fbie4eaco_jessy-kurczewski_625x300_16_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-found-guilty-of-murdering-friend-by-spiking-her-water-bottle-with-eye-drops-4578381%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kurczewski%20tearfully%20reacted%20as%20the%20verdict%20was%20announced%20in%20the%20Waukesha%20County%20court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-found-guilty-of-murdering-friend-by-spiking-her-water-bottle-with-eye-drops-4578381%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-found-guilty-