eate%20an%20escape%20tunnel%20for%20the%20workers%2C%20who%20are%20all%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESteel%20pipes%20are%20being%20used%20to%20supply%20oxygen%20and%20small%20food%20items%20into%20the%20tunnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeavy%20drilling%20equipment%20has%20been%20flown%20in%20from%20Delhi%20which%20can%20clear%20nearly%205%20metres%20of%20debris%20every%20hour.%20The%20drill%20is%20commonly%20used%20to%20form%20boreholes%20in%20rock%2C%20soil%2C%20and%20other%20subsurface%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20an%20effective%20substitute%20for%20jobs%20that%20may%20require%20hours%20if%20done%20manually.%20It%20is%20usually%20used%20to%20drill%20holes%20ranging%20between%201%20metre%20to%2030%20metres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drill%20has%20a%20rotational%20blade%2C%20called%20auger%2C%20which%20is%20fixed%20to%20a%20drill%20stem.%20Rescuers%20in%20Uttarakhand%20have%20already%20set%20up%203%20auger%20drills%20and%20will%20soon%20deploy%20three%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20are%20confident%20that%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20get%20the%20trapped%20workers%20out%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEfforts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20make%20a%20safety%20passage%20or%20a%20small%20tunnel%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20pipe.%20Material%20has%20been%20made%20available%20at%20the%20site.%20The%20platform%20is%20also%20being%20made%20for%20them.%20After%20that%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20escape%20tunnel%20will%20also%20be%20started.%20Everyone%20is%20said%20to%20be%20safe%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Uttarakhand%20District%20Magistrate%20Abhishek%20Rohilla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tunnel%2C%20which%20is%2013%20metres%20wide%20(43%20feet)%20and%2015%20metres%20(50%20feet)%20in%20height%20with%20the%20workers%20trapped%20in%20a%20two-kilometre%20space%2C%20was%20being%20built%20on%20a%20national%20highway%20that%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Char%20Dham%20Yatra%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pace%20of%20drilling%20had%20slowed%20down%20du