0Chinese%20added%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bunrealistic%20for%20one%20side%20to%20remodel%20the%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20warned%20the%20Taiwan%20question%20was%20among%20the%20most%20%26quot%3Bsensitive%20issues%20in%20the%20relationship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20will%20realize%20reunification%2C%20and%20this%20is%20unstoppable%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20highlighted%20the%20restoration%20of%20direct%20military-to-military%20contacts%2C%20saying%20they%20would%20prevent%20miscalculations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20and%20also%20indicted%20he%20had%20the%20ability%20to%20speak%20to%20Xi%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20how%20accidents%20happen%2C%20misunderstandings%2C%20so%20we're%20back%20to%20direct%2C%20open%2C%20clear%2C%20direct%20communications%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20preserve%20and%20pursue%20high-level%20diplomacy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BTo%20keep%20the%20lines%20of%20communication%20open%2C%20including%20between%20President%20Xi%20and%20me.%20He%20and%20I%20agreed%20that%20each%20one%20has%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20phone%20call%20directly%20and%20be%20heard%20immediately.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20shares%20trading%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20lost%20as%20much%20as%202%25%20in%20Thursday%20morning%20trading%20Beijing%20time.%20The%20onshore%20yuan%20weakened%200.17%25%20at%207.2592%20per%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaders%20of%20the%20world's%20two%20largest%20economies%20had%20not%20spoken%20for%20a%20year.%20Both%20sides%20celebrated%20the%20meeting%2C%20which%20lasted%20over%20four%20hours%2C%20as%20productive%2C%20and%20a%20step%20toward%20normalizing%20a%20relationship%20battered%20by%20a%20series%20of%20diplomatic%20and%20economic%20clashes.%20The%20agreements%20though%20largely%20roll%20back%20steps%20China%20took%20following%20former%20House%20Speaker%20Nancy%20Pelosi's%20trip%20to%20Taiwan%20-%20made%20over%20the%20objection%20of%20Beijing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20he%20trusted%20Xi%2C%20Biden%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BTrust%20but%20verify%20as%20the%20old%20saying%20goes%2C%20that's%20where%20I%20am.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20the%20US%20intended%20to%20%26quot%3Bcompete%20vigorously%26quot%3B%20with%20China%2C%20but%20added%20%26quot%3Bwe'll%20manage%20that%20competition%20responsibly%2C%20so%20it%20doesn't%20veer%20into%20conflict%20or%20accidental%20conflict.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20ended%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20though%2C%20Biden%20referred%20to%20Xi%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdictator%2C%26quot%3B%20repeating%20remarks%20that%20sparked%20criticism%20from%20China%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20he%20is.%20He's%20a%20dictator%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20he's%20a%20guy%20who%20runs%20a%20country%20that%20is%20a%20communist%20country%20that's%20based%20on%20a%20form%20of%20government%20totally%20different%20than%20ours%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChoreographed%20Summit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20off-the-cuff%20remark%20followed%20a%20day%20of%20carefully%20choreographed%20meetings%20that%20saw%20the%20two%20leaders%20meet%20on%20the%20sweeping%20grounds%20of%20the%20Filoli%20estate%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Woodside%2C%20about%2025%20miles%20south%20of%20San%20Francisco.%20The%20summit%20went%20multiple%20sessions%20and%20included%20a%20working%20lunch%20featuring%20herb%20ricotta%20ravioli%2C%20heritage%20chicken%20and%20almond%20meringue%20cake%2C%20as%20the%20pair%20and%20top%20aides%20huddled%20in%20a%20secluded%20century-old%20Georgian%20manor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20saw%20an%20extended%20discussion%20of%20foreign%20policy%2C%20with%20US%20officials%20saying%20they%20believe%20Xi%20indicated%20he%20wasn't%20readying%20plans%20for%20a%20mass%20invasion%20of%20Taiwan.%20Biden%20asked%20the%20Chinese%20to%20respect%20the%20electoral%20process%20in%20the%20island's%20upcoming%20presidential%20vote%2C%20the%20officials%20said%2C%20speaking%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20said%20he%20reiterated%20the%20US's%20One%20China%20policy%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bthat%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20change%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20officials%20also%20pressed%20Chinese%20counterparts%20to%20discuss%20the%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20with%20Iran%2C%20which%20financially%20supports%20the%20militant%20group%20categorized%20as%20a%20terrorist%20organization%20by%20the%20US%20and%20EU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20from%20China%20on%20combating%20fentanyl%20was%20characterized%20by%20senior%20US%20officials%20as%20the%20most%20important%20agreement%20from%20the%20summit.%20The%20officials%20said%20Biden%20told%20Xi%20that%20fentanyl%20posed%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20drug%20problems%20the%20US%20had%20faced.%20The%20officials%20said%20they%20would%20watch%20closely%20to%20see%20if%20China%20follows%20through%20on%20the%20pledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20said%20the%20agreement%20helps%20%26quot%3Bsignificantly%20reduce%20the%20flow%20of%20precursor%20chemicals%20and%20pill%20presses%20from%20China%20to%20the%20Western%20Hemisphere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20save%20lives%20and%20I%20appreciate%20President%20Xi's%20commitment%20on%20this%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20to%20recharge%20senior%20military-to-military%20communications%20was%20also%20high%20on%20the%20agenda%20following%20a%20series%20of%20close%20encounters%20between%20Chinese%20and%20American%20ships%20and%20planes%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20agreed%20to%20policy%20level%20discussions%20with%20US%20Defense%20Secretary%20Lloyd%20Austin%2C%20as%20well%20as%20operational%20engagements%20at%20senior%20military%20levels%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US%20officials.%20That%20restores%20communications%20channels%20China%20halted%20last%20year%20to%20protest%20Pelosi's%20visit%20to%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20US%20officials%20have%20pushed%20hard%20to%20resume%20the%20talks.%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20detailed%20a%20Chinese%20jet's%20intercept%20of%20a%20US%20B-52%20in%20international%20airspace%20over%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20during%20Foreign%20Minister%20Wang%20Yi's%20recent%20visit%20to%20Washington%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlinken%20noted%20the%20table%20he%20and%20Wang%20were%20sitting%20at%20was%2010%20feet%20-%20the%20same%20space%20between%20the%20two%20aircraft%20during%20the%20incident%20-%20to%20highlight%20the%20need%20to%20restore%20communications%20to%20prevent%20conflict%2C%20according%20to%20the%20person%2C%20who%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20said%20the%20two%20countries%20had%20agreed%20to%20manage%20disagreements%20more%20effectively%20and%20have%20more%20dialogues%20and%20consultations%20to%20avoid%20misunderstandings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20that%20they%20appreciate%20each%20other's%20principles%20and%20red%20lines%2C%20and%20refrain%20from%20flip-flopping%2C%20being%20provocative%2C%20and%20crossing%20the%20lines%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20agreed%20to%20a%20dialogue%20to%20keep%20the%20emerging%20technology%20from%20being%20deployed%20in%20ways%20that%20could%20destabilize%20global%20security%2C%20according%20to%20US%20officials.%20The%20meeting%20also%20saw%20an%20agreement%20to%20work%20to%20increase%20flights%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20next%20year%2C%20according%20to%20Xinhua%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20summit%2C%20the%20US%20and%20China%20als