0Tetwali%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Namita%20Namdev%20Bhurkood%20learned%20one%20of%20the%20more%20emphasised%20roles%20growing%20up%20%E2%80%94%20being%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332396%2Fhow-to-make-bio-enzymes-from-kitchen-waste-at-home-diy-steps-by-kolkata-gardener-nita-singh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egood%20homemaker.%20%3C%2Fa%3EWhat%20she%20did%20not%20realise%20for%20a%20long%20time%20was%20that%20she%20could%20also%20be%20the%20breadwinner%20of%20a%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20rightly%20puts%20it%2C%20life%20is%20mostly%20about%20%E2%80%9Crediscovering%20yourself%E2%80%9D%20every%20other%20day.%20Now%2C%20she%20finds%20herself%20in%20more%20than%20one%20role%20%E2%80%94%20a%20mother%2C%20a%20homemaker%2C%20a%20bamboo%20artist%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20president%20of%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20self-help%20group%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20group%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317348%2Fmangal-shetty-sustainable-home-in-aghanashini-karnataka-panchabhuta-conservation-foundation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etransforms%20bamboo%20into%20beautiful%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3Ekandils%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sky%20lanterns)%2C%20phone%20holders%2C%20%3Cem%3Erakhis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20dustbins%2C%20photo%20frames%2C%20carts%2C%20hangers%2C%20keychains%20and%20much%20more.%20Recently%2C%20she%20led%20a%20group%20of%20seven%20women%20at%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20India%20to%20showcase%20their%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20felt%20like%20we%20were%20in%20a%20movie.%20There%20were%20leaders%20and%20influential%20people%20all%20around%20us.%20Never%20in%20my%20dreams%20had%20I%20imagined%20that%20I%20would%20be%20in%20a%20place%20like%20that%2C%20let%20alone%20lead%20a%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20Namita%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%