espite%20them%20being%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20read%20such%20personal%20stories%20of%20war%2C%20it%20makes%20you%20understand%20what%20people%20went%20through%20and%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20a%20country%2C%20that%20was%20nurtured%20by%20the%20sacrifices%20of%20people%2C%20for%20granted.%20Her%20story%20is%20inspirational%20for%20young%20women.%20For%20%3Cem%3Edadi%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eit%20was%20only%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20that%20people%20started%20giving%20her%20recognition.%20This%20book%20has%20gotten%20some%20attention%20to%20her%20story%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanvi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20even%20went%20the%20extra%20mile%20to%20collate%20various%20photographs%20and%20letters%20written%20in%20classic%20Japanese%20language%20and%20the%20INA%20archives%20to%20put%20together%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Tanvi%E2%80%99s%20home%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20bedtime%20stories%20are%20centered%20around%20Asha%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%20freedom%20movement.%20Her%20children%20take%20pride%20in%20singing%20%3Cem%3EKadam%20Kadam%20Badhaye%20Ja.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Tanvi%20Srivastava.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699626225000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334021%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Inspired%20by%20Netaji%20Bose%2C%20Asha%20Sahay%20was%2017%20when%20she%20joined%20INA's%20Rani%20of%20Jhansi%20regiment%20and%20fought%20for%20Indian%20independence.%20Her%20great-granddaughter-in-law%2C%20Tanvi%20Srivastava%2C%20has%20documented%20her%20incredible%20story%20in%20the%20book%20'The%20War%20Diary%20of%20Asha-san'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IIT